Vole Magic Note v3.11

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Vole Magic Note is a subset of Vole Media CHM, lets you craft stunning multimedia notes that contain images, audio, video, and links to online resources every day.

When you are writing a journal or meeting minute, you may want to add some images, audio, video, YouTube video or some other web resources and even websites.

Vole Magic Note can make notes everyday, add all these resources into your notes and preview them in embedded media player.

Powerful search feature allows you to not miss anything.

Vole Magic Note is simple and powerful.
